casebody.data:
Hogan, Appellant, v. Kavanaugh et al., Respondents. (Supreme Court, General Term, Fifth Department. April 13, 1892.) Action by Phoebe J. Hogan against Daniel Kavanaugh and others.

Argued before Dwight, P. J„ and Macomber and Lewis, JJ.

No opinion. Judgment appealed from affirmed, with costs.
